text: Kushal Punjabi (23 April 1977 â€“ 26 December 2019) was an Indian actor. He won the TV reality game show, Zor Ka Jhatka: Total Wipeout, the Indian version of the American game show Wipeout in February 2011. Punjabi had been in movies such as Lakshya, Kaal and in Ssshhhh...Phir Koi Hai. He had also appeared in television shows such as Ishq Mei Marjawan.
